show.description: When Tasha loses everything, her husband, company, and daughter—she finds an unexpected ally in a man hiding a deadly secret. Shelter in the Mafia is a wild ride of betrayal, power games, and love blooming in the heart of chaos. What starts as survival, ends in a war between heart and heritage. Watch Now.
